# API Workflow

Before changing models or API usage:

1. **OpenAPI**: Use `external_docs/openapi-swagger.json` (or sync via `.github/scripts`). Check required/optional, types, read-only, masking.
2. **User-docs from sitemap**: `https://docs.endorlabs.com/sitemap.xml`; local copy in `external_docs/user-docs/` if synced via `.github/scripts`.
3. **Implementation**: Align Pydantic with spec; test masked and unmasked responses; keep backward compatibility.

Drift and docs: see `docs/rules-of-engagement/docs-drift-workflow.md`. Run `python .github/scripts/unified_docs_workflow.py --all` to refresh.
